Botines first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/> Prior to the [[2010 U.S. census]], four CDPs ([[Bonanza Hills, Texas|Bonanza Hills]], [[Four Points, Texas|Four Points]], [[Los Veteranos II, Texas|Los Veteranos II]], and [[Sunset Acres, Texas|Sunset Acres]]) were in full or in part carved out of its territory.<ref name=2010CensusTX/>

